  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p class="mt-md">
            SiRelations was founded with a simple belief: artificial intelligence
            should be accessible to every business, not just tech giants.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-md">
            Based in the Netherlands, we combine deep technical expertise with
            practical business understanding. We don't just build AI solutions ‚Äî
            we help you understand them, implement them, and get real value from them.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-md">
            Our approach is pragmatic and results-focused. We cut through the hype
            to deliver AI solutions that actually work for your specific needs
            and constraints.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-visual">
          <div class="value-cards">
            <div class="value-card">
              <span class="value-icon">üéØ</span>
              <h3>Pragmatic</h3>
              <p>Focus on real results, not buzzwords</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <span class="value-icon">ü§ù</span>
              <h3>Collaborative</h3>
              <p>We work with you, not just for you</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <span class="value-icon">üîí</span>
              <h3>Trustworthy</h3>
              <p>GDPR compliant, transparent, reliable</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <span class="value-icon">üöÄ</span>
              <h3>Forward-thinking</h3>
              <p>Always learning, always improving</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section mission-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-content text-center">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mission-statement mt-lg">
          "To democratize artificial intelligence by making powerful AI solutions
          accessible, understandable, and valuable for businesses of all sizes."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>Based in the Netherlands</h2>
        <p class="mt-md">
          We're proud to be a Dutch company, operating within the EU regulatory
          framework and committed to the highest standards of data protection and privacy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="location-features mt-xl">
        <div class="location-feature">
          <h3>üá™üá∫ EU-Based</h3>
          <p>Operating within European regulations and standards</p>
        </div>
        <div class="location-feature">
          <h3>üîê GDPR Compliant</h3>
          <p>Full compliance with EU data protection requirements</p>
        </div>
        <div class="location-feature">
          <h3>üåç Global Reach</h3>
          <p>Serving clients across Europe and beyond</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Want to work with us?</h2>
      <p class="mt-md">We'd love to hear about your project.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-lg">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-small h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hero-small p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .value-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .mission-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .mission-statement {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: var(--space-lg) auto 0;
  }

  .location-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .location-feature {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .location-feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .value-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .location-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
